{"type": "article", "id": 16290, "title": "25 Lamp", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 111, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135545H219PxeJuzKCowdF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯的木质灯罩由 25 片组成，因而名叫 25 Lamp ，来自瑞典的 Kovac Family。每一片都在灯泡上面的连接处固定，依次拉开形成一个球体，层层相叠，是一个有层次感的灯笼。光照强度能通过灯罩的开合做调整，看似传统，却很有现代的设计感。灯罩是手工做的，可以选择橡树、白蜡木和桦树。<a href=\"http://store.kovacfamily.com/collections/numbers/products/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143625JyYrVS7DPIRCzG1v.gif\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143630N6moxpj9rXvi0HD2.jpg\" width=\"931\" height=\"1280\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37486574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143631ndJzeMt8loBrcpfs.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143631U1hP76oQkGdZRWNc.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}